@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### 実装済み機能

###
## GET /folders
GET {{baseUrl}}/folders
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ja


###

## POST /folders
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "D:\\ビデオ"
}

###

## POST /folders (既存フォルダの復旧)
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "C:\\Users\\user\\Videos"
}

###

## 4. フォルダを削除（ソフトデリート）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/folders/1
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

###

## 5. フォルダ一覧を確認（削除後）
GET {{baseUrl}}/folders
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

###

## 6. 複数フォルダを追加
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "D:\\Movies"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "E:\\Downloads"
}

###
http://localhost:8000/api/v1/files/1/hibi01.mp4

## 7. Windowsアニメフォルダの例（Docker経由でのマウントパス）
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "/mnt/d/デスクトップ/アニメ/年別/3/15"
}

###

## 8. ネットワークパスの例
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "path": "\\\\SERVER\\share\\folder"
}

###

## 7. 英語でのテスト
GET {{baseUrl}}/folders
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: en

###

## 8. 無効なフォルダIDで削除を試みる
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/folders/99999
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

###

## 9. 不正なリクエストボディで追加を試みる
POST {{baseUrl}}/folders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ja

{
  "invalid_key": "some_value"
}

###
